description: City: Sarasota, FLFresh Baja Mexican Gourmet Food Truck, VOTED #1 FOODTRUCK IN SARASOTA for two years in a row 2014 & 2015 ,serves up everything from Lobster Tacos to Quesadillas, Tortas, Salads and Bowls. Don't forget to ask about our daily specials and what is the grilled fish of the day. We also offer a wide selection of Gluten Free options.Vegan, Vegetarian... No problem. We've got that too. Yes we do catering!!!!!!.Baja Boys Grill isn't any ordinary food truck. We are FRESH, ORGANIC, HOT, and DELICIOUS! Stop in today for one of our delicious daily special menu items, an enormous 1lb burrito, or one of our tasty baja salads. Choose from chicken, pork, steak, or beef! Or even fish!You're taste buds will be delighted!
name: Baja Boys Grill
